      "author": "goryugocast",
      "description": "First release prepared for the official Obsidian community plugins directory submission.\n\n## What's new\n\n- **Edit Time Score** for daily notes — co-occurrence based on file mtime with exponential decay\n- **Per-strategy Excluded Folders** — exclusions now apply consistently across Graph, Metadata, Time, and EditTime strategies\n- **Async scoring API** — `AtomicInsights.getRelatedNotes()` (via CDP/CLI) no longer blocks the UI thread on large vaults\n- **ESLint setup** with strict TypeScript rules\n\n## Scoring spec\n\nSee [docs/SCORING.md](https://github.com/goryugocast/atomic-insights/blob/main/docs/SCORING.md) for the full per-strategy semantics.",
